Definition: lacking in harmony or compatibility or appropriateness
Example: a plan incongruous with reason; incongruous behavior; a joke that was incongruous with polite conversation
Synonyms: noun, attribute, incongruousness, incongruity, CONGRUOUS, lacking, in, harmony, or, compatibility, appropriateness, a, plan, incongruous, with, reason, behavior, joke, that, was, polite, conversation
Category: adj.all
